  "body": "Right now parts of the config can be modified after the HRE has been initialized, for example, from a task. This is useful, at least for now, when we are growing the plugin system.\r\n\r\nNot all the config can be overwritten though, as some objects keep references to its values, and not to the config object.\r\n\r\nWe should create a policy about this and document it.\r\n\r\nFor an example about this, take a look at this other issue: https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/issues/1030#issuecomment-736289457",
